metadata.name: Paving a Path towards Solitude
metadata.description: Three Steps Ahead. 2023 March #000. Walking down the lonely path, away from bustling crowds, eager to find solitude at last. Alone on my journey, adrift in a sea of thought, destination still unknown. At the crossroads of life, awe and anticipation overwhelm, forging ever onwards. Parallel paths stretch wide, leading to unknown endings, where I can be set free. Snapshots of the future, show me whatâ€™s three steps ahead, on my way to true solitude.
